TextSection.Contents: A rare genetic intellectual disability characterized by the association of intellectual disability with variable other anomalies in the absence of a well-characterized syndrome. Associated abnormalities may include facial dysmorphism neurological signs and symptoms behavioral problems and abnormalities of various other organ systems.
